---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-content">
    <p>
      <a href="https://github.com/jonathan-vella/azure-agentic-infraops" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Agentic InfraOps
      </a>
      — Azure infrastructure engineered by AI agents.
    </p>
    <p class="footer-meta">
      <a href="https://github.com/jonathan-vella/azure-agentic-infraops/blob/main/LICENSE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MIT License</a>
      <span class="footer-sep">·</span>
